# Git Rules

## Branch Naming
- feature/{ticket}-{desc}, fix/{ticket}-{desc}
- hotfix/{desc}, release/v{version}, refactor/{area}

## Commits (Conventional)
- Format: `type(scope): subject`
- Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
- Subject: max 50 chars, imperative mood
- Footer: reference issues (Closes #123)

## Pull Request
- Title: conventional commit format
- Size: < 400 lines preferred
- All tests must pass
- Require 1+ approval
- Squash if messy commits

## Branch Protection
- main: protected, require PR
- Delete branches after merge
